            "dc:publisher": "Natural Environment Research Council",
            "dc:description": "List of float battery types. Argo netCDF variable BATTERY_TYPE syntax uses both R33 altLabel and R34 altLabel with the following convention: <R33-battery_maker> <R34-battery_type> <voltage> V [+<R33-battery_maker> <R34-battery_type> <voltage> V]. Argo netCDF variable BATTERY_PACKS uses both R35 altLabel and R34 prefLabel with the following convention: <x><R35-battery_size> <R34-battery_type> [+<x><R35-battery_size> <R34-battery_type>].",
            "dc:title": "Argo battery type",
